            <title>[WICKET-5123] Component.continueToOriginalDestination() can redirect to ./.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-5123</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Following scenario:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Home page redirects to login page via RestartResponseException if no user is logged in.&lt;br/&gt;
The user logs in, and is led back to the originally called page via continueToOriginalDestination().&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If the original page was the home page, Wicket&apos;s UrlRenderer produces a target url of ./. here (which IE browsers can&apos;t handle).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
